How to make it precisely?
1. gcc -o server server.c
2. gcc -o client client.c

and then ./server
and then ./client

1. Write the function to make decision by passing the destip and routing table.

2. Write the function to print out the statistic file.

3. Error Handeling, sleep when 2 packets are generated.

What to do in 2b?:

Server is done, Just need to modify it to make it fit the client.